data.description: Charming Panama City Property with Endless PossibilitiesWelcome to your new home in beautiful Panama City! This property boasts a spacious 24x30X10 pole barn, providing you with the perfect space for all your storage needs and hobbies. Additionally, you'll find a convenient 12x20 shed w/power and an attached 24x20 covered carport area for parking.Features at a Glance:Well pump for irrigation, ensuring a lush and vibrant garden.Very well-kept carpeting throughout the home, offering a fresh and inviting atmosphere.Enjoy year-round comfort with a brand-new HVAC system.A huge fenced-in yard with ample space for a future pool or additional buildings, making it an entertainer's dream.Location, Location, LocationSituated in a fantastic neighborhood and only 5 blocks from a walk along St. Andrew Bay. This property offers the ideal combination of tranquility and convenience. Even a dog and walking park at the end of the street. You'll have quick and easy access to both 23rd Street and 15th Street, ensuring that you're never far from shopping, dining, and entertainment options.Versatile Utility RoomOne of the standout features of this home is the generous 15x15 utility room located just off the kitchen. This versatile space can be customized to meet your needs, whether you're looking to create an additional bedroom, a home office, a playroom, or a crafting haven. The possibilities are endless!Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Panama City property your own. With its fantastic location, spacious yard, and versatile spaces, it's the perfect place to call home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and explore the potential of this remarkable property.
